## Input

```css
@supports (#{$name}:) {
  .a {
    color: red;
  }
}

@supports not (#{$name}:) {
  .a {
    color: red;
  }
}

@supports (margin-#{$side}:) {
  .b {
    color: blue;
  }
}

@supports (#{$name}:) or (display: grid) {
  .b {
    color: blue;
  }
}

@supports (--theme-#{$slot}:) {
  .c {
    color: green;
  }
}

```


